    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270610/extras/b010b1b3205edaf540190c402e3dc3b9.webp?t=1706755288\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><br><strong>对于那些令你恐惧的东西，你是选择视而不见，还是勇敢直面？</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270610/extras/0476082f3beaf16204df308544e37534.poster.avif?t=1706755288\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270610/extras/0476082f3beaf16204df308544e37534.webm?t=1706755288\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270610/extras/0476082f3beaf16204df308544e37534.mp4?t=1706755288\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>《厌山夜话》取材于本土怪谈和都市传说，</strong><br><strong>是一款融合了卡牌战斗要素，剧情丰富的现代志异RPG。</strong><br><br><strong>在《厌山夜话》中，玩家将扮演不信邪的保险推销员杭世麒，</strong><br><strong>因为一场发生在中元节的葬礼，而迷失在一栋没有出口的筒子楼中。</strong><br><br><strong>在怪力乱神重返阳间的夜晚里，一位自称是“故人之女”的神秘小女孩出现在主角面前，</strong><br><strong>希望他挑起驱魔人的重担。</strong><br><strong>一段充满谜团与悬念的故事就此展开……</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270610/extras/b41900024f6dd035083f6ff68ffccd98.webp?t=1706755288\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270610/extras/da13cdabf9bcd36af8c9f15db4976a30.poster.avif?t=1706755288\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270610/extras/da13cdabf9bcd36af8c9f15db4976a30.webm?t=1706755288\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270610/extras/da13cdabf9bcd36af8c9f15db4976a30.mp4?t=1706755288\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>在游戏中，您将探索筒子楼中的巨大箱庭式迷宫，<br>穿过没有尽头的走廊，空无一人的水房，荒废已久的游乐屋等熟悉景象。</strong><br><br><strong>在数百个精心设计的鬼打墙场景中，<br>您将会找到各种朴素但实用的消耗道具，蕴藏奇妙力量的压胜物，以及不知何人留下的神秘讯息……</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270610/extras/70a651e51d6f9721cfca045820196165.webp?t=1706755288\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270610/extras/63242c66783d106f8e45b1cbfc66be68.poster.avif?t=1706755288\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270610/extras/63242c66783d106f8e45b1cbfc66be68.webm?t=1706755288\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270610/extras/63242c66783d106f8e45b1cbfc66be68.mp4?t=1706755288\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>制作组从都市传说、志怪小说与新怪谈中获得灵感，为游戏带来了70种以上的怪物。</strong><br><br><strong>它们各自拥有着奇异怪诞的超自然力量，只要将其击败，就能获得蕴含怪物力量的独特卡牌。<br>每击败一只新的怪力乱神，便给您的牌组带来了更多的可能性。</strong><br><br><strong>您可以像策略卡牌游戏那样自由构筑自己的驱邪卡组，完成独一无二的“爬楼”挑战。<br>但要小心，使用这些卡牌，也许会潜移默化地影响主角对这个世界的认知……</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270610/extras/610d4587da1b391afe5ce9a880327b02.webp?t=1706755288\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270610/extras/73a005b6e2175f9e7a29964d02cec0dc.poster.avif?t=1706755288\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270610/extras/73a005b6e2175f9e7a29964d02cec0dc.webm?t=1706755288\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2270610/extras/73a005b6e2175f9e7a29964d02cec0dc.mp4?t=1706755288\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>受困于大楼之中的倒霉蛋并不止主角一人，<br>尝试与他们交流情报，获得逃出生天的线索。<br>但或许其中有人已被怪力乱神蛊惑，正在假装好心地将你引入陷阱……</strong>",
